The evidence with the title 'Obama has waited longer for cabinet confirmations than any ... ' says Apr 23, 2015  ... Obama nominees hold the top three spots on the waiting list . And Obama has had to wait longer , on average, than any other president in the data set for his nominees to join his cabinet : confirmed Obama nominees have waited for an average of 35 days . George W. Bush's waited for an average of 16 days  ... 
